thread.title: Eleanor Grant
thread.title_full: Ace Rental Cars Australia & New Zealand reviewed by Eleanor Grant

author: Eleanor Grant
title: Eleanor Grant
text: Ace Rentals have always been my go to rental car company. Their customer service is always fantastic. They go out of their way to be accommodating and ensure everything is perfect. They are the most reasonably priced by far and this is my biggest reason for always choosing them over any other.
